# G-endpoint — add a REST endpoint to an existing controller

Run `gofasta g endpoint <Resource> <METHOD> <path> --dry-run --json`
first (e.g. `gofasta g endpoint Order POST /orders/{id}/archive`).

Surface the controller/service/route changes, then re-run without
`--dry-run` to apply if approved. Run `gofasta swagger` after to
refresh OpenAPI docs.
